%h3 What kind of integration does the application offer?

%p.checkbox
  = f.check_box :offers_login
  %label{:for=>"client_application_offers_login"} Users can login to your application using their Manybots Account
  
%p.checkbox
  = f.check_box :offers_exports
  %label{:for=>"client_application_offers_exports"} Users can post their activities on your app to their Manybots Account

%p.checkbox
  = f.check_box :offers_reading
  %label{:for=>"client_application_offers_reading"} Users can visualize activities from their Manybots Account
  

